TO SECURE THIS SYSTEM:
  1. Change SSH password:    sudo passwd cupcake
  2. Change web password:    Go to web interface → Admin → Users
  3. Setup SSH keys:         ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
  4. Enable firewall:        sudo ufw enable
  
